comments: Thybulle (PHI) makes marginal contact with Bullock's (NYK) front during his drive into the lane and as he passes the ball.
Horford (PHI) makes some contact with Robinson's (NYK) right forearm during the dunk attempt, but it is marginal and Robinson is able to move through it to finish at the rim.
Richardson (PHI) makes marginal contact with his off-arm to Robinson's (NYK) front as he releases to change direction at the end of the drive.
Bullock (NYK) makes marginal contact with Horford's (PHI) left arm as he moves to defend the entry pass.
Harris (PHI) and Richardson (PHI) each make marginal contact with Randle's right arm during his drive into the lane.
Randle (NYK) leaves his feet and returns to the floor without losing control of or releasing the ball.
Simmons (PHI) legally continues his dribble after momentarily losing control of the ball along the perimeter.
Horford (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Payton's (NYK) path and does not deliver the contact, some of which may occur to Payton's leg.
Simmons (PHI) briefly has his arm around Morris Sr.'s (NYK) midsection before correcting.
Simmons (PHI) fails to inbound the ball within five seconds.
Payton (NYK) makes marginal contact with Harris' (PHI) midsection after he receives the pass.
Simmons (PHI) and Morris Sr. (NYK) engage and disengage off-ball.
Morris Sr. (NYK) establishes his left foot as his pivot, which he moves from heel-to-toe to create distance.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in Simmons' (PHI) path and does not deliver the contact.
Simmons (PHI) cleanly dislodges Randle (NYK) of the ball along the sideline.
Simmons (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball as he simultaneously makes marginal contact with Randle's (NYK) left forearm. Harris (PHI) then cleanly dislodges Randle of the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that Randle (NYK) last touched the ball before it went out of bounds.
Bullock (NYK) commits the take foul on Richardson (PHI).
Payton (NYK) commits the take foul on Korkmaz (PHI).
Korkmaz (PHI) and Morris Sr. (NYK) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Korkmaz (PHI) commits the take foul on Morris Sr. (NYK).
Richardson (PHI) and Harris (PHI) legally contest Morris Sr.'s (NYK) jump shot attempt.
